properties.headline: High Wind Watch issued February 17 at 1:47PM CST until February 19 at 9:00AM CST by NWS Midland/Odessa TX
properties.description:
* WHAT...East winds sustained at 35 to 45 mph possible.

* WHERE...Guadalupe and Delaware Mountains in Texas, mainly
Guadalupe Pass.

* WHEN...From Tuesday afternoon through Wednesday morning.

* IMPACTS...High winds could make driving difficult for motorists
driving high profile vehicles such as campers, vans, and
tractor trailers.
properties.instruction:
Monitor the latest forecasts and warnings for updates on this
situation. Fasten loose objects or shelter objects in a safe
location prior to the onset of winds.

NWSheadline: HIGH WIND WATCH IN EFFECT FROM TUESDAY AFTERNOON THROUGH WEDNESDAY MORNING
